   <concept id="FAR_5_201" class="- topic/topic concept/concept " xtrc="">
      <title class="- topic/title ">
         <ph class="- topic/ph " props="autonumber">5.201</ph> General.</title>
      <conbody class="- topic/body  concept/conbody ">
         <ol id="d324e13" class="- topic/ol ">
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d338e10">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph> As required by the Small Business
Act (<xref href="http://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=granuleid:USC-prelim-title15-section637(e)&amp;num=0&amp;edition=prelim"
                        scope="external"
                        format="html">15 U.S.C. 637(e)</xref>) and
the Office of Federal Procurement Policy Act (<xref href="http://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=granuleid:USC-prelim-title41-section1708&amp;num=0&amp;edition=prelim"
                        scope="external"
                        format="html">41 U.S.C. 1708</xref>), agencies
must make notices of proposed contract actions available as specified
in paragraph (b) of this section.</p>
            </li>
            <li props="Runin" class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d338e21">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>
               </p>
               <ol id="d324e38" class="- topic/ol ">
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p " id="d338e26">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph> For
acquisitions of supplies and services, other than those covered
by the exceptions in <xref href="5.202.dita#FAR_5_202"
                              base="i1120688"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">5.202</xref> and
the special situations in <xref href="5.205.dita#FAR_5_205"
                              base="i1120807"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">5.205</xref>,
the contracting officer must transmit a notice to the GPE, for each
proposed-</p>
                     <ol id="d324e54" class="- topic/ol ">
                        <li class="- topic/li ">
                           <p class="- topic/p " id="d338e38">
                              <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(i)</ph> Contract action meeting the threshold
in <xref href="5.101.dita#FAR_5_101"
                                    base="i1120993"
                                    outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                                    class="- topic/xref ">5.101</xref>(a)(1);</p>
                        </li>
                        <li class="- topic/li ">
                           <p class="- topic/p " id="d338e46">
                              <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(ii)</ph> Modification
to an existing contract for additional supplies or services that
meets the threshold in <xref href="5.101.dita#FAR_5_101"
                                    base="i1120993"
                                    outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                                    class="- topic/xref ">5.101</xref>(a)(1);
or</p>
                        </li>
                        <li class="- topic/li ">
                           <p class="- topic/p " id="d338e54">
                              <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(iii)</ph> Contract
action in any amount when advantageous to the Government.</p>
                        </li>
                     </ol>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p " id="d338e59">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph> When transmitting
notices using electronic commerce, contracting officers must ensure
the notice is forwarded to the GPE.</p>
                  </li>
               </ol>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d338e64">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(c)</ph> The primary
purposes of the notice are to improve small business access to acquisition
information and enhance competition by identifying contracting and
subcontracting opportunities.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d338e69">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(d)</ph> The GPE
may be accessed via the Internet at 
                     <xref href="https://www.sam.gov"
                        format="html"
                        scope="external"
                        class="- topic/xref ">https://www.sam.gov</xref>.
               </p>
            </li>
         </ol>
      </conbody>
   </concept>
